CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 18, 1957, pg. A17, reads: "Daffodil Baby Contest - Pictured here are the first, second and fourth prize-winners in the Daffodil Club's recent baby contest. Left to right, first: Toy Annette with her mother, Mrs. Marion Williams. Second winner: Phyllis Marie with her mother, Mrs. Bernell Copeland. Fourth winner was Sharon Saunders, daughter of Mrs. Louise Saunders. Third was Curtis Tibbs, whose mother is Mrs. Lottie Tibbs. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Daffodil Club baby contest winners from left: Toy Annette Williams with Marion Williams, Phyllis Marie Copeland with Bernell Copeland, and Sharon Saunders with Louise Saunders
